## Method B — Delta (EP-Frequency Weighted)

**Axis:** Direct Estimation  
**Parameters:** 0 free (uses shared theta + episode EP proportions)

```
FUNCTION fit(data):
    theta    = global_theta(data)
    delta[e] = mean of EP flags over all lines in episode e   -- shape (E, P)
    RETURN theta, delta

FUNCTION predict(line, theta, delta):
    e   = episode of line
    w   = delta[e]                        -- EP proportions for episode e
    w   = w / sum(w)                      -- normalise (guard: sum + 1e-12)
    RETURN sum over i of (w[i] * mean of theta row i across K skills)

NOTE (CV): delta for test episodes uses their own EP structure only
           (no skill labels involved → no leakage)
```

**Key property:** Episode-constant within each episode. Weights by how
frequently each EP appears in that episode rather than treating all
active EPs equally.

