## Shared Evaluation — AIC and BIC

```
-- Computed at LINE level using a common external logistic model.
-- Makes AIC comparable across all 11 methods on the same scale.

PROCEDURE compute_aic_bic(epspi_column, k_method):
    total_ll = 0
    FOR each Skill_j:
        fit LogisticRegression(Skill_j ~ EPSPI_n) at LINE level
        p_n      = predicted probability for each line n
        log_lik  = sum(Y_nj * log(p_n) + (1-Y_nj) * log(1-p_n))
        total_ll += log_lik

    k_total = k_method + 2 * K     -- method params + 2 per skill (slope+intercept)
    AIC     = 2 * k_total - 2 * total_ll
    BIC     = k_total * log(N) - 2 * total_ll
    RETURN AIC, BIC
```

