## Notation Reference

| Symbol | Meaning |
|---|---|
| N | Total number of lines (19,181) |
| E | Number of episodes (49) |
| P | Number of Education Practices (3) |
| K | Number of skills (4) |
| X_ni | Binary flag: EP i active in line n |
| Y_nj | Binary flag: Skill j present in line n |
| θ_ij | P(Skill_j=1 \| EP_i=1), Laplace-smoothed |
| EPSPI_n | Line-level index ∈ [0,1] (except Method K) |
| EPSPI_e | Episode mean of EPSPI_n |
| Ȳ_e | Observed episode skill rate (ground truth) |
| ε_e | Residual: Ȳ_e − EPSPI_e |
| α | Laplace smoothing constant = 1 |

